Name:         spacefill
Version:      0.1
Cabal-version: >= 1.8
License:      PublicDomain
Author:       Raphael 'kena' Poss
Maintainer:   knz@thaumogen.net
Synopsis:     Generators for space-filling curves.
Category:     Algorithms
Homepage:     https://github.com/knz/spacefill

Description:
   Generators of Hilbert and Moore space-filling curves in configurable
   coordinate domains.

Build-type: Simple

Library
   Build-depends: base >= 4.0 && < 5
   Exposed-modules: Data.SpaceFillingCurves
   GHC-Options: -Wall

Test-Suite doc-tests
   Build-depends: base
   Type: exitcode-stdio-1.0
   Main-is: README.lhs

Source-repository head
   Type: git
   Location: git://github.com/knz/spacefill
